<br>
2. Instead of sending all the TANKS including Paladins, the leader sent all Heavy tanks and then after a while decided to send the PALADIN Death Squad group...  Hummm why not send all the TANKS including Paladins ?? <br>
<br>
3.  Now me being level 47...  Almost every mob resisted me (( IG and Icy Terrors for example ?? Why... some are blue but still resisted everything i threw at them even Malisement !<br>
<br>
4. And Vox well...  RESIST after RESIST...  <br>
<br>
5. So for me being level 47... was i too low ??  Or what did i do wrong ?  <br>
